msgid ""
"<1.so>I'm talking about <2.se_co>the sword that seals\n"
"the darkness<3.re_co>, of course! Legend has it\n"
"that it's hidden somewhere in Hyrule!\n"
"<4.so>A single swing shoots out sacred light\n"
"beams...<5.pa>mows down wicked monsters...<6.pa>\n"
"and restores peace and stuff...\n"
"Ahhhh, it's every dreamer's dearest\n"
"dream come true, I tell ya!"
msgstr ""

