"that seals the darkness<3.re_co>?<4.pa> Yeah, what if?!\n"
"That'd be swell...\n"
"<5.so>I could use the sword's sacred light to\n"
"beat the stuffing out of every single\n"
"monster on the <6.se_co>Hebra Mountains<7.re_co>!"
msgstr ""

