msgctxt "talk_0052"
msgid ""
"<1.so>HUH?! That's the <2.se_co>sword that seals \n"
"the darkness<3.re_co>? I can't believe it!\n"
"\n"
"<4.so>Deep breaths... Deeeeep breaths...<5.pa>\n"
"OK. I see, I see... <6.pa>Hmmm...\n"
"\n"
"<7.so>Honestly, it's a tad slimmer than\n"
"I imagined.\n"
"\n"
"Since it's the legendary sword,\n"
"I thought it would be as big as me!\n"
"With, like...jewels everywhere.\n"
"<8.so>Wow, it's still amazing, though. I can feel\n"
"the power.<9.pa> Hey, thanks for showing that\n"
"to me! I'll never forget this day!"
msgstr ""

