msgid ""
"<1.so>If the legends are true, the <2.se_co>sword that\n"
"seals the darkness <3.re_co>is the blade of the\n"
"chosen hero... <4.pa>Are YOU that hero?!\n"
"If so, you'll likely face many hardships\n"
"in your life...but never give up!\n"
"Promise me that."
msgstr ""

